snippet.title: Omega Strike Trailer
snippet.description:
Out now on Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/680340/Omega_Strike/
Omega Strike is a metroidvania game with multiple playable characters. Unlock new abilities for each of your heroes in your battle against the mutant hordes of Doctor Omega.

Website: http://www.omegastrike.com/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/woblyware
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/woblyware
